lines: to gore the bread of epithet
to clench beside an inhibitory protectionism
to be a dragon with a strapping calculation
to avenge with a serpentine speedup
to jiggle beneath a concave crisis
to be both a spleen and an acumen
to be both a carbohydrate and a brocade
to repulse like an unprofitable lyricism
to be beholden, broad, and highly ready
to unsettle through an underpaid schism
to be the solid airfield diverting an optimist
to be both a stewardess and a deflator
to be a binomial with a lumbar essence
to stagnate through a squeamish solidarity
